---
const npmUrl = 'https://www.npmjs.com/package/@codexa/cli';
const githubUrl = 'https://github.com/sayam-1705/codexa';
const docsUrl = 'https://github.com/sayam-1705/codexa/blob/main/docs/README.md';
---

<section class="section hero">
  <div class="copy">
    <p class="eyebrow mono">PUBLISHED ON NPM - CODEXA CLI v1.0.0</p>
    <h1>Pre-commit guardrails that focus on the code you actually changed.</h1>
    <p class="sub">
      Codexa helps teams ship cleaner commits without punishing them for legacy noise. Run blame-aware
      checks, review issues in an interactive terminal UI, apply fast fixes, and keep your quality workflow
      local-first with optional Ollama suggestions.
    </p>

    <div class="install card">
      <code id="installCmd">npm install -g @codexa/cli</code>
      <button type="button" id="copyInstall">Copy</button>
    </div>

    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn primary" href={npmUrl}>Install from npm</a>
      <a class="btn" href={githubUrl}>View on GitHub</a>
      <a class="btn ghost" href={docsUrl}>Read the docs</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <aside class="heroCard card">
    <p class="label mono">Why teams pick Codexa</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Blocks issues introduced in your diff instead of inherited debt.</li>
      <li>Supports JavaScript, TypeScript, and Python out of the box.</li>
      <li>Works in local commits, team config flows, and GitHub Actions CI.</li>
      <li>Exposes adapter hooks so you can extend it for more languages.</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="meta">
      <span>CLI command: <code>codexa</code></span>
      <span>Package: <code>@codexa/cli</code></span>
    </div>
  </aside>
</section>

<script>
  const copyBtn = document.getElementById('copyInstall');
  const installCmd = document.getElementById('installCmd');
  if (copyBtn && installCmd && navigator.clipboard) {
    copyBtn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      await navigator.clipboard.writeText(installCmd.textContent || 'npm install -g @codexa/cli');
      copyBtn.textContent = 'Copied';
      setTimeout(() => {
        copyBtn.textContent = 'Copy';
      }, 1200);
    });
  }
</script>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.5fr) minmax(280px, 0.9fr);
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: end;
    padding-top: 32px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 0.98;
    max-width: 12ch;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .sub {
    max-width: 64ch;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .install {
    margin-top: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    gap: 12px;
    background: rgba(8, 12, 26, 0.82);
  }

  .install code {
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
    color: var(--text-strong);
  }

  .install button {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 8px 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 140ms ease, border-color 140ms ease;
  }

  .install button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
  }

  .actions {
    margin-top: 18px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .btn {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 11px 16px;
    transition: transform 140ms ease, border-color 140ms ease, background 140ms ease;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
  }

  .btn.primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-strong));
    color: #1a1308;
    border-color: transparent;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .btn.ghost {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  }

  .heroCard {
    padding: 22px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.15), transparent 34%),
      rgba(10, 14, 28, 0.88);
  }

  .label {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: var(--muted-strong);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .heroCard ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--text-strong);
  }

  .meta {
    margin-top: 18px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      max-width: 14ch;
    }
  }
</style>
